  "title": "Product Engineer | Mechanical | CAD / SolidWorks | Marine and Offshore",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a <strong>Marine and Offshore Industry.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a <strong>Product Engineer </strong>to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West </strong>- easily accessible.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>Mechanical Design & Development:</strong></p><ul><li>Translate product and system requirement into manufacturable mechanical designs, ensuring performance, safety, and production feasibility.</li><li>Develop and test prototypes, analyze results, and refine designs to enhance reliability, performance, and manufacturability throughout the product lifecycle.</li></ul><p><strong>Machinery Arrangement & Layout Planning:</strong></p><ul><li>Design machinery layouts to optimize space, accessibility, safety, and ease of maintenance.</li><li>Plan and coordinate equipment placement to support efficient manufacturing processes.</li></ul><p><strong>Product Research & Concept Development:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct research to identify user needs, market trends, and product requirements.</li><li>Generate detailed design concepts and prototypes using CAD and SolidWorks.</li><li>Create comprehensive mechanical designs, including drawings, models, BOMs, and specifications.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Mechanical Engineering, Industrial Design, or a related field. </li><li>At least 2 years of experience in mechanical product design. </li><li></li><li>Proficiency in CAD software (e.g., SolidWorks, AutoCAD).</li></ul><p><em>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click </em><em><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></em><em> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</em><br /><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</em></p><p><em>Email Address: </em><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</em></a></p><p><em>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</em><br /><em>EA License No: 19C9682</em><br /><em>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</em></p>",
